languages.text: "Верно говорите! Но я была юной и дурной, думала только, как нарушителя повяжу".
"You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."
languages.original_text: "Верно говорите! Но я была юной и дурной, думала только, как нарушителя повяжу".

traits.locale_text: "You are not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I would wrangle the trespasser."
"You are not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I would wrangle the trespasser."
"You are not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might apprehend the trespasser."
"You are not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might apprehend the trespasser."
"You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

languages.text: "Ihr habt nicht unrecht! Aber ich war jung und dumm und dachte nur daran, den Täter zu schnappen."
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr habt nicht unrecht! Aber ich war jung und dumm und dachte nur daran, den Täter zu schnappen."

languages.text: «¡No se equivoca! Pero era joven e imprudente, y no pensaba en otra cosa que en aprehender al responsable».
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

traits.locale_text: «¡No se equivoca! Pero era joven e imprudente, y no pensaba en otra cosa que en aprehender al responsable».

languages.text: 「確かにそうです！ですが私は若く知恵不足で、犯人を捕まえる方法など他に思いつかなかったのです」
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

traits.locale_text: 「確かにそうです！ですが私は若く知恵不足で、犯人を捕まえる方法など他に思いつかなかったのです」

languages.text: “您说得没错！可我当时既年轻、又鲁莽，一心只想着怎么抓住那个犯人。”
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

traits.locale_text: “您说得没错！可我当时既年轻、又鲁莽，一心只想着怎么抓住那个犯人。”

languages.text: « Vous n'avez pas tort ! Mais j'étais jeune et écervelée. Je ne pensais qu'à la façon de prendre le coupable la main dans le sac. »
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."

traits.locale_text: « Vous n'avez pas tort ! Mais j'étais jeune et écervelée. Je ne pensais qu'à la façon de prendre le coupable la main dans le sac. »

languages.text: "Haksız sayılmazsınız! Ancak o zamanlar genç ve ahmaktım. Aklımdan yalnızca suçluyu nasıl yakalayabileceğim geçiyordu."
languages.original_text: "You're not wrong! But I was young and foolish, and thought only of how I might nab the culprit."
